posts.post_content:
We search for the arcane.

Years ago on ebay, I wondered where the best venue was, where the guys who sold them to me got them from.
I did find Net54--Mecca, nirvana?--a collector's oasis.
And I've learned a lot and made many good deals, and even ... friends? ... at least people like me.
But still we quest for the source
of the magic

at a bargain, of cour$e,
We collectors.

Doug
